{
  "texts": [
    "By implementing essential information sharing between RL agents, 32 expands on this work.",
    "The authors presented three new traffic controllers-TC-SBC, TC-GAC, and TCSBC+GAC.",
    "To determine the traffic conditions at nearby intersections, TC-SBC adds a small quantity of congestion.",
    "TC-GAC selects the best course of action based on this information.",
    "Tested algorithms on essential grid networks fared well in varying traffic scenarios."
  ]
}